        <mxCell id="N0zKVQGEHYRE-DV4ys3H-40" value="&lt;h1&gt;Power Domains&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Power switch is on VDD.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Isolation cells are on output ports&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Logic outside the powerdomain blocks is always on.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Before switching off power ensure there are no outstanding transactions on AXI.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;All domains are turned on at POR. Arm will turn of the Hyperbus/chiplet domain based on chipmode&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="nCs7eCHHcYqx8qUM5zFF-1">
